NORTH ATLANTIC.
DNC 19.
DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED ON 406 MHZ FROM ROWING VESSEL,
ONE PERSON ON BOARD, WITHIN FIVE MILES OF
50-56.43N 025-59.36W AT 060819Z AUG.
VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO MRCC SOLENT,
PHONE: 44 2392 552100, FAX: 44 1329 244547,
E-MAIL: SOLENT-CG@HMCG.GOV.UK.
